### Data Management
Data-related documentation covers:
- Data sources configuration (`sources.yaml`, `source-catalog.yaml`)
- Data destinations (`destination-catalog.yaml`)
- Audience management (`audiences.yaml`)
- PII handling (`pii_integrations.yaml`)
